{"surahDetails":{"id":96,"arabicName":"العلق","banglaName":"রক্তপিণ্ড","englishName":"The Clot","enTranslatedName":"Al-'Alaq","arLocation":"مكية","enLocation":"meccan","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio-surah/128/ar.alafasy/96.mp3","totalAyah":19},"surah":{"id":96,"verses":[{"id":1,"arabic_text":"ٱقۡرَأۡ بِٱسۡمِ رَبِّكَ ٱلَّذِي خَلَقَ","bangl_text":"পাঠ করুন আপনার পালনকর্তার নামে যিনি সৃষ্টি করেছেন","english_text":"Recite in the name of your Lord who created","page":597,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6107.mp3","colorText":"ٱ[q:7699[قْ]رَأْ بِ[h:13285[ٱ]سْمِ رَبِّكَ [h:14559[ٱ]لَّذِى خَلَ[q[ق]َ","juz":30,"ruku":538,"manzil":7,"htmlColorText":"ٱ<span class=qalaqah>قْ</span>رَأْ بِ<span class=ham_wasl>ٱ</span>سْمِ رَبِّكَ <span class=ham_wasl>ٱ</span>لَّذِى خَلَ<span class=qalaqah>ق</span>َ <span class=end>١</span>"},{"id":2,"arabic_text":"خَلَقَ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنَ مِنۡ عَلَقٍ","bangl_text":"সৃষ্টি করেছেন মানুষকে জমাট রক্ত থেকে।","english_text":"Created man from a clinging substance","page":597,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6108.mp3","colorText":"خَلَقَ [h:7324[ٱ]لْإِ[f:5969[نس]َ[n[ـٰ]نَ مِنْ عَلَ[q[ق]ٍ","juz":30,"ruku":538,"manzil":7,"htmlColorText":"خَلَقَ <span class=ham_wasl>ٱ</span>لْإِ<span class=ikhafa>نس</span>َ<span class=madda_normal>ـٰ</span>نَ مِنْ عَلَ<span class=qalaqah>ق</span>ٍ <span class=end>٢</span>"},{"id":3,"arabic_text":"ٱقۡرَأۡ وَرَبُّكَ ٱلۡأَكۡرَمُ","bangl_text":"পাঠ করুন, আপনার পালনকর্তা মহা দয়ালু","english_text":"Recite, and your Lord is the most Generous","page":597,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6109.mp3","colorText":"ٱ[q:7699[قْ]رَأْ وَرَبُّكَ [h:14560[ٱ]لْأَكْرَمُ","juz":30,"ruku":538,"manzil":7,"htmlColorText":"ٱ<span class=qalaqah>قْ</span>رَأْ وَرَبُّكَ <span class=ham_wasl>ٱ</span>لْأَكْرَمُ <span class=end>٣</span>"},{"id":4,"arabic_text":"ٱلَّذِي عَلَّمَ بِٱلۡق