 ر</span>َّءَاهُ <span class=ham_wasl>ٱ</span>سْتَغْنَىٰٓ <span class=end>٧</span>"},{"id":8,"arabic_text":"إِنَّ إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ ٱلرُّجۡعَىٰٓ","bangl_text":"নিশ্চয় আপনার পালনকর্তার দিকেই প্রত্যাবর্তন হবে।","english_text":"Indeed, to your Lord is the return","page":597,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6114.mp3","colorText":"إِ[g[نّ]َ إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ [h:14566[ٱ][l[ل]رُّ[q:14567[جْ]عَىٰٓ","juz":30,"ruku":538,"manzil":7,"htmlColorText":"إِ<span class=ghunnah>نّ</span>َ إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ <span class=ham_wasl>ٱ</span><span class=laam_shamsiyah>ل</span>رُّ<span class=qalaqah>جْ</span>عَىٰٓ <span class=end>٨</span>"},{"id":9,"arabic_text":"أَرَءَيۡتَ ٱلَّذِي يَنۡهَىٰ","bangl_text":"আপনি কি তাকে দেখেছেন, যে নিষেধ করে","english_text":"Have you seen the one who forbids","page":597,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6115.mp3","colorText":"أَرَءَيْتَ [h:14568[ٱ]لَّذِى يَنْهَىٰ","juz":30,"ruku":538,"manzil":7,"htmlColorText":"أَرَءَيْتَ <span class=ham_wasl>ٱ</span>لَّذِى يَنْهَىٰ <span class=end>٩</span>"},{"id":10,"arabic_text":"عَبۡدًا إِذَا صَلَّىٰٓ","bangl_text":"এক বান্দাকে যখন সে নামায পড়ে","english_text":"A servant when he prays","page":597,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6116.mp3","colorText":"عَ[q:3317[بْ]دًا إِذَا صَلَّىٰٓ","juz":30,"ruku":538,"manzil":7,"htmlColorText":"عَ<span class=qalaqah>بْ</span>دًا إِذَا صَلَّىٰٓ <span class=end>١٠</span>"},{"id":11,"arabic_text":"أَرَءَيۡتَ إِن كَانَ عَلَى ٱلۡهُدَىٰٓ","bangl_text":"আপনি কি দেখেছেন যদি সে সৎপথে থাকে।","english_text":"Have you seen if he is upon guidance","page":597,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6117.mp3","colorText":"أَرَءَيْتَ إِ[f:2594[ن ك]َانَ عَلَى [h:4019[ٱ]لْهُدَىٰٓ","juz":30,"ruku":538,"manzil":7,"htmlColorText":"أَرَءَيْتَ إِ<span class=ikhafa>ن ك</span>َانَ عَلَى <span class=ham_wasl>ٱ</span>ل